dct_title_s: [Τοπογραφικοί χάρται της Ελλάδος & Βαλκανίων] / Γεογραφική Υπηρεσία Στρατού.
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by form lines and spot heights. Some sheets show hachures. Principal meridian is Ferro. Bookseller's label pasted on verso: K. Grigouras & Sie., Athens, Greece. Κ. Γρεγουρας & Σια. Maps were trimmed on top and bottom. Map title, scale, legend, and distributor labels are pasted on verso.
